<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(فَغَمَهُ الطِّيبُ،<span class="c5"> كَمَنَعَ فَغْمًا وفُغُومًا:</span> سَدَّ خَيَاشِيمَهُ)</span> ،<span class="c5"> وَفِي الحَدِيثِ:</span> " لَوْ أَنَّ امْرأَةً<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>